title: Sabrina Carpenter, SZA, Ariana Grande Win Multiple Awards at 2025 Kids’ Choice Awards (Full Winners List) - Billboard
summary: Sabrina Carpenter emerged as the top winner at the 2025 Kids’ Choice Awards, securing three Orange Blimp trophies, including favorite female breakout artist and favorite album for 'Short n’ Sweet'.
why_matters: The 2025 Kids’ Choice Awards highlighted popular artists and their influence on young audiences, with Sabrina Carpenter, SZA, and Ariana Grande achieving significant recognition.
